icedDrink.name: Caramel Macchiato
icedDrink.description: A perfect balance of coffee, vanilla, milk, and caramel makes a sweet and creamy summer drink.

icedDrink.name: Nitro Cold Brew
icedDrink.description: This innovative concoction is essentially cold brew coffee imbued with nitrogen gas.

icedDrink.name: Vietnamese Coffee
icedDrink.description: This coffee has a delightful hint of chocolate flavor and is made using robusta coffee beans, along with a phin.

icedDrink.name: Iced Latte
icedDrink.description: Renowned for their harmonious blend of frothed milk, foam, and espresso, possess a cold counterpart in iced lattes.

icedDrink.name: Mazagran
icedDrink.description: Citrus might not be the first flavor that springs to mind when considering coffee, but a foray into the world of Algerian mazagran will convince you of its enjoyable compatibility.

icedDrink.name: Frappucino
icedDrink.description: Made famous by Starbucks, the Frappuccino is a blended iced coffee drink that’s topped with whipped cream and syrup.

icedDrink.name: Strawberry and Cream
icedDrink.description: Frappuccino crème syrup blended with milk, strawberry sauce and ice. Topped with whipped cream.

icedDrink.name: Spanish Latte
icedDrink.description: Iced coffee drink that's made with milk (any kind, I ordered soy milk), condensed milk, and fresh espresso.

icedDrink.name: Iced Mocha
icedDrink.description: An espresso-based drink with chocolate and warm milk for the right blend of creaminess and sweetness, served over ice.

icedDrink.name: Iced Chocolate
icedDrink.description: It's easy, super chocolate-y, and hydrating. Plus, it's got a rich enough chocolate flavor that it's something that you'll sip slowly.

hotDrink.name: Matcha Latte
hotDrink.description: Made from finely ground green tea leaves that are mixed with steamed milk.

hotDrink.name: Hot Chocolate
hotDrink.description: made with dark, semisweet, or bittersweet chocolate grated or chopped into small pieces and stirred into milk with the addition of sugar.

hotDrink.name: Hot Toddy
hotDrink.description: It's a quick solve to a chilly evening that simply requires hot water, honey, lemon, and whiskey!

hotDrink.name: Pumpkin Spice Latte
hotDrink.description: Made with real pumpkin puree—this latte is a must-have when the weather turns chilly.

hotDrink.name: Chai Latte
hotDrink.description: Made by mixing steamed milk with black tea that has been infused with spices

hotDrink.name: Caramel Latte
hotDrink.description: A velvety coffee indulgence featuring freshly brewed espresso, steamed milk, and a generous drizzle of luscious caramel syrup.

hotDrink.name: Caffè Americano
hotDrink.description: A classic favorite prepared by diluting an espresso with hot water, giving it a similar strength to, but different flavor from, traditionally brewed coffee.

hotDrink.name: Hot buttered rum
hotDrink.description: Mixed drink containing rum, butter, hot water or cider, a sweetener, and various spices.

hotDrink.name: Irish Coffee
hotDrink.description: A caffeinated alcoholic drink consisting of Irish whiskey, hot coffee and sugar, which has been stirred and topped with cream.

hotDrink.name: Asiático Coffee
hotDrink.description: Coffee with condensed milk and cognac; a few drops of Licor 43 as well as a couple of coffee beans, lemon rind and cinnamon may be added.

cakes.name: Pancakes
cakes.description: A breakfast dish, a flat cake that's made by pouring batter into a hot pan and frying it on both sides. Many people like to eat their pancakes with a drizzle of maple syrup.

cakes.name: Carrot Cake
cakes.description: A sweet and moist spice cake, full of cut carrots and toasted nuts, and covered in cream cheese icing.

cakes.name: New York Cheesecake
cakes.description: This easy, foolproof cheesecake recipe creates a dense, rich, and creamy dessert with irresistible flavor—perfect for any occasion and sure to impress.

cakes.name: Vegan Chocolate Cake
cakes.description: This ultra lush and rich vegan chocolate cake is the definition of decadence with a soft and tender moist crumb.

cakes.name: Tunisian Orange Cake
cakes.description: Made with fresh orange and ground almonds, this Tunisian Orange Cake is a masterpiece whilst also being probably the simplest cake ever.

cakes.name: Choc Chip Pecan Pie
cakes.description: Pie of pecan nuts mixed with a filling of eggs, butter and sugar.

cakes.name: Key Lime Pie
cakes.description: Made of Key lime juice, egg yolks, and sweetened condensed milk.

cakes.name: Red Velvet Cake
cakes.description: Tangy and buttery, with a mild cocoa and sweet vanilla flavor.

cakes.name: Strawberry Shortcake
cakes.description: A tender vanilla cake filled with layers of whipped cream frosting and juicy strawberries.

cakes.name: Molten Lava Cake
cakes.description: A French dessert that consists of a chocolate cake with a liquid chocolate core.

pastries.name: Tarte Tatin
pastries.description: Dark and sticky caramel, sweet apples and crisp pastry combine to make this heavenly French dessert.

pastries.name: Pain au chocolat
pastries.description: A Yeasted puff pastry dough wrapped around a stick of chocolate

pastries.name: Tiramisu
pastries.description: Classic Italian dessert renowned for its heavenly layers of coffee-soaked ladyfingers and velvety mascarpone cream.

pastries.name: Croissant
pastries.description: A laminated, yeast-leavened bakery product that contains dough/roll-in fat layers to create a flaky, crispy texture.

pastries.name: Cinnamon Roll
pastries.description: Made with yeasted dough that is rolled into a rectangle, spread with butter, then sprinkled heavily with a mix of sugar and cinnamon and rolled into a log that is cut into slices.

pastries.name: Everything Bagel
pastries.description: The bagel underneath the everything topping is just a plain bagel—until it's transformed by the addition of a spice mix right before it's baked.

pastries.name: Glazed Donut
pastries.description: Light and fluffy, covered in a simple glaze.

pastries.name: Danish Pastry
pastries.description: Made with laminated dough, where the dough is repeatedly covered with butter and folded over itself.

pastries.name: Éclair
pastries.description: These elongated pastries with an appealing glaze, a crispy exterior, a soft doughy interior, and a sweet, creamy center

pastries.name: Baklava
pastries.description: Luscious dessert created with layers of thin phyllo dough intertwined with chopped nuts, all doused in a sweet, viscous syrup.

pasta.name: Lasagne
pasta.description: Layered with a rich meat sauce and a creamy parmesan white sauce, plus the perfect amount of mozzarella cheese.

pasta.name: Carbonara
pasta.description: Italian main course consisting of spaghetti with bacon and a creamy sauce made from eggs, Pecorino or Parmesan and black pepper.

pasta.name: Chili prawin linguine
pasta.description: Pasta tossed with a rich tomato sauce with a tingle of spicy heat and plump prawns (shrimp).

pasta.name: Macaroni Cheese
pasta.description: The dish consists of macaroni (short, tubular) pasta, baked in a cheesy bechamel sauce (also known as a Mornay sauce) in the oven.

pasta.name: Aglio Olio
pasta.description: Deliciously simple Italian dish of fresh garlic, olive oil, and Parmesan cheese tossed with freshly cooked spaghetti.

pasta.name: Baked Penne With Chicken and Sun-Dried Tomatoes
pasta.description: It has chicken breasts, mushrooms, and sun-dried tomatoes. Shredded provolone and grated Parmesan make it super creamy.

pasta.name: One-Pan Creamy Tuna Pasta
pasta.description: This one-pot wonder inspired by Tuna Helper has tuna, tender noodles, and peas cooked together in a creamy sauce.

pasta.name: Mushroom Ragu
pasta.description: A hearty and deeply flavorful mushroom ragù featuring finely chopped mushrooms, tomatoes, white wine, and aromatics slow-cooked in an oven.

pasta.name: Garlic Cream Sauce Ravioli
pasta.description: Sauce is made to be drenched over ravioli and compliments so many different fillings.

pasta.name: Beef Stroganoff
pasta.description: Features juicy beef, hearty mushrooms, mustard, white wine, and sour cream for the most tender and delicious results.

mains.name: Tonkatsu Pork
mains.description: A pork chop breaded with flour, egg, and Panko (bread crumbs), then deep fried.

mains.name: Sweet and Sour Pork
mains.description: A Chinese stir-fry dish made with juicy pieces of pork tenderloin, bell peppers, onion, and pineapple.

mains.name: Roasted Pork Belly
mains.description: This roasted pork belly is juicy and succulent with a crispy crackling layer on top that takes it to the next level.

mains.name: Kung Pao Chicken
mains.description: Chinese-style stir-fried chicken cubes with dried chili peppers.

mains.name: General Tso's Chicken
mains.description: Perfect combination of sweet, savoury, spicy and tangy with crispy Chinese chicken bites.

mains.name: Thai Green Curry
mains.description: Undoubtedly a unique curry of all since it gives the soup a light green colour and incredible flavour, making it stand out from the rest.

mains.name: Beef Caldareta
mains.description: Beef stew cooked with tomato sauce and liver spread.

mains.name: Szechuan Beef
mains.description: Spicy stir fry made with tender pieces of beef and colorful vegetables, all tossed in a sweet and savory sauce.

mains.name: Beef Brisket Pot Roast
mains.description: It's essentially a pot roast—a slow braise with lots and lots of onions.

mains.name: Baked salmon with fennel & tomatoes
mains.description: Aniseedy fennel and juicy cherry tomatoes cut through the richness of salmon fillets.

mains.name: Kung Po Prawns
mains.description: A delicious stir fry that combines jumbo shrimp in a salty almost sweet sauce loaded with dried chillies, Szechuan pepper and peanuts.

mains.name: Fried Calamari
mains.description: Crispy, succulent calamari rings, coated in seasoned flour and quickly fried to crispy perfection.

sides.name: Prawn & Fennel Bisque
sides.description: This smooth and creamy seafood soup made with saffron and fennel makes an impressive starter or light supper.

sides.name: Cream of Mushroom Soup
sides.description: Full flavoured with garlic, onions and herbs, subtle enough to shine through and compliment the natural flavour of the mushrooms.

sides.name: Shakshouka
sides.description: a Maghrebi (North African) dish, popular throughout the region, featuring poached eggs in a spicy tomato sauce, seasoned with peppers, onion, garlic, and various spices.

sides.name: Poutine
sides.description: Dish of french fries and cheese curds topped with a brown gravy.

sides.name: Cheesy Beef Nachos
sides.description: Cheesy Beef Nachos are a classic appetizer staple that's perfect for Solo munching, or turn into a sharing platter for the holidays or parties!

sides.name: Ceasar Salad
sides.description: Made with romaine lettuce, croutons, Parmesan cheese, and Caesar dressing.

sides.name: Cheesy Garlic Bread with dip
sides.description: Roasted garlic and shallots in a creamy cheesy dip with fresh herbs like parsley and chives, served with toasty bread.

sides.name: Mozarella Sticks
sides.description: This classic appetizer consists of sticks of mozzarella cheese that are coated in seasoned Italian breadcrumbs, then deep fried until golden brown.

sides.name: Chicken Parm Sliders
sides.description: Succulent store-bought rotisserie chicken layered with tangy marinara sauce, gooey mozzarella cheese, and fragrant fresh basil, all nestled between soft, pillowy dinner rolls.

sides.name: Clam Chowder
sides.description: Creamy broth that’s loaded with delicious clams, savory bacon, simple seasonings, and perfectly cooked potatoes.
